# 📝 Responsive Student Marksheet System

A clean, responsive web application that allows educators to input marks for multiple students and automatically generate totals, percentages, and grades. This tool provides a fast, browser-based solution to manage academic performance data for small classes or training sessions.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

- 🔹 **Responsive UI** – Optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices
- 🔹 **Dynamic Calculations** – Automatically computes:
  - Subject-wise total
  - Percentage
  - Grade based on defined criteria
- 🔹 **User-Friendly Inputs** – Easily enter student names and marks
- 🔹 **Lightweight & Fast** – Built with HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript (no external dependencies)

---

## 🎯 Use Cases

- Classroom student performance tracking
- Teacher-made grading tools
- Training centers, coaching classes, and tuition institutions
- Developer UI/logic practice

---

## 📊 Grading Criteria

| Percentage Range | Grade  |
|------------------|--------|
| 80% - 100%       | A+     |
| 70% - 79%        | A      |
| 60% - 69%        | B      |
| 50% - 59%        | C      |
| 40% - 49%        | D      |
| Below 40%        | F      |

